  description: Increases Attack Speed by 20% and Health by 40. At the start of combat,
    the wearer and all adjacent allies gain 20% bonus Attack Speed for the remainder
    of the battle. An ivory-trimmed quiver blessed by the Goddess of the Woodlands;
    it magically produces exactly the right projectile at the right moment, allowing
    an entire squad to rain down fire with impossible coordination.
